{"tid":2344640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部：包括達賴喇嘛在內的活佛轉世，都應遵守国家法律法規","createTime":"2020-12-29T02:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T17:36:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"585d6ff7cf668ac7f06d14306b9ed6a9590e956c","tid":2344640,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2020/1229/U617P22T1D870559F1DT20201229092750.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2020%2F1229%2FU617P22T1D870559F1DT20201229092750.jpg&h=43847dfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據中國外交部網站12月28日消息，中國外交部發言人趙立堅主持當天例行記者會。<br />\n<br />\n　　會上，日本共同社記者提問，據報道，美國領導人27日簽署的有關法案中包含&ldquo;西藏政策與支持法案&rdquo;，其中涉及達賴喇嘛接班人的問題。請問中國如何選定達賴的繼任和轉世？中方對美方的涉藏法案有何評論？<br />\n<br />\n　　趙立堅：既然你問到有關活佛轉世的問題，我願意借此機會重申中方有關立場。活佛轉世是藏傳佛教特有的傳承方式，有固定的宗教儀軌和歷史定制。中國政府實行宗教信仰自由政策，頒布有《宗教事務條例》和《藏傳佛教活佛轉世管理辦法》，尊重和保護藏傳佛教這一傳承方式。達賴喇嘛活佛轉世係統已經有幾百年的歷史，十四世達賴喇嘛本人就是按照宗教儀軌和歷史定制尋訪認定，報請當時的中央政府批準繼位的。因此，包括達賴喇嘛在內的活佛轉世，都應該繼續遵守國家法律、法規，遵循宗教儀軌、歷史定制。<br />\n<br />\n　　至於你提到美方有關涉藏法案，中方對此表示堅決反對。涉藏問題事關中國主權和領土完整，純屬中國內政，不容任何外部勢力干涉。中國政府維護國家主權、安全、發展利益的決心堅定不移。我們敦促美方停止借涉藏問題插手中國內政，不得實施有關法案中針對中國、損害中方利益的消極內容和條款，以免進一步損害中美合作和兩國關係大局。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://www.hkcna. hk/content/2020/1229/870559.shtml</code></pre>"},{"pid":"3f7f3d5c0b0833fd3a82453427162ff5b77a50a7","tid":2344640,"uid":127575,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:21:41.000Z","msg":"所有世界都係中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a993518e3c6a00f4bb7da9d1859803e9c4ad9a","tid":2344640,"uid":115096,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:24:58.000Z","msg":"首先你是中國人，轉世也是中國人。"},{"pid":"ea17887a6c2ba5071d60f9d64c08efe77aa67151","tid":2344640,"uid":4942,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:27:03.000Z","msg":"人地西藏不嬲唔承認你個垃圾國家<br />\n<br />\n又要被中國人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80963bf4258dd09802355fd25ccc5fa0eebfff0","tid":2344640,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c440e79e17208e7d1d01c23c203dbe346394c212","tid":2344640,"uid":126731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:28:54.000Z","msg":"耶蘇都要幫雜種奶袋底"},{"pid":"54be9dc8d7fd6ab7267128e4464aef2e2d298e0d","tid":2344640,"uid":83523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:29:31.000Z","msg":"佢真係當自己係神？"},{"pid":"35481e267d3b195037cb8523a69e0b0e10d2f0e1","tid":2344640,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:29:36.000Z","msg":"無神論學咩人講宗教"},{"pid":"5da7c59d8bb81218c73d9e89fbb67f7d67beb722","tid":2344640,"uid":217049,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:30:52.000Z","msg":"神權君授<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5fd3966e6a839afd0f90e2ae4a8fc7bcb852b79","tid":2344640,"uid":247892,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5da7c59d8bb81218c73d9e89fbb67f7d67beb722","tid":2344640,"uid":217049,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:30:52.000Z","msg":"神權君授<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成件事好撚古怪<br />\n又活佛又要守法"},{"pid":"4d9203dc573d0439e07275607310dc88e591c88f","tid":2344640,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046570c1f3f67fc36ca92eb05105efe689829817","tid":2344640,"uid":310446,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:36:16.000Z","msg":"轉世管理法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed1be2531b6de46e6adfa5cc590e56237249ec2","tid":2344640,"uid":274772,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:16:24.000Z","msg":"銀河系 佢管<br />\n<br />\n連陰間都管埋 <br />\n<br />\n勁"},{"pid":"4b4471b3715e719c2d98e6af8fdc793467f600ac","tid":2344640,"uid":131836,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:23:04.000Z","msg":"活佛如需轉世<br />\n請先填寫轉世申請書<br />\n並交有關部門審批<br />\n任何未經批准之轉世 均屬違法<br />\n違者可被判終身監禁<br />\n並且剝奪轉世權利終生<br />\n活佛切勿以身試法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9346a207c39bda8e1ab8b3e5b13b3529faf01fd0","tid":2344640,"uid":274772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4b4471b3715e719c2d98e6af8fdc793467f600ac","tid":2344640,"uid":131836,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:23:04.000Z","msg":"活佛如需轉世<br />\n請先填寫轉世申請書<br />\n並交有關部門審批<br />\n任何未經批准之轉世 均屬違法<br />\n違者可被判終身監禁<br />\n並且剝奪轉世權利終生<br />\n活佛切勿以身試法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:26:58.000Z","msg":"仲有閻羅王在批准活佛轉世時亦要取得中央人民政府批文<br />\n並由中央人民政府任命"},{"pid":"543948ea76dd358e01fad37ffcc647b13c431d56","tid":2344640,"uid":8308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:29:15.000Z","msg":"教宗需習帝加冕"},{"pid":"4f93f60b7e424d14f7d83cd43087de239598f143","tid":2344640,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:29:29.000Z","msg":"串到佛祖都要企埋一邊<br />\n真係唔知有無佛祖<br />\n但如果有，佛祖出唔出手?"},{"pid":"39014f8251d6545e0092057471d674c4ef7d7833","tid":2344640,"uid":50101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:39:46.000Z","msg":"活佛VIVA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df8a022ed12c76296c3d0edfe733a79bf9c761b","tid":2344640,"uid":137897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:58:14.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">關你老母共狗撚事咩</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"22a0083063e66960be46351578a3280bc091e89b","tid":2344640,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T04:14:50.000Z","msg":"活佛要交版權稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3f3a28cffe6ea084347b4a7c9b1f4e0e92e707","tid":2344640,"uid":274772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T04:18:54.000Z","msg":"由陰間轉世要隔離14日 自費於支那九流賓館"},{"pid":"8841da7f09e5c3ab8f99e9d440a0a7efbe3901e3","tid":2344640,"uid":131205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f93f60b7e424d14f7d83cd43087de239598f143","tid":2344640,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:29:29.000Z","msg":"串到佛祖都要企埋一邊<br />\n真係唔知有無佛祖<br />\n但如果有，佛祖出唔出手?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"佛教講因果同福報<br />\n唔見有報應，通常係佢前世有積福、而家扣緊<br />\n同埋果報時機未成熟，可能下世/下下世先報<br />\n<br />\n所以有啲人一出世就好淒慘（被父母虐待、被人折磨、國家打仗...）都係因為要還上世/上幾世啲業債<br />\n<br />\n所以唔使佛祖出手，佢將來自然要受報應<br />\n話唔定到時仲要求佛祖打救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1578aaae1bd332d9373468b0c9f4031977f2ba","tid":2344640,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T05:02:34.000Z","msg":"中國政府實行宗教信仰自由政策，頒布有《宗教事務條例》和《藏傳佛教活佛轉世管理辦法》，尊重和保護藏傳佛教這一傳承方式。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸拆撚晒d教堂/佛像<br />\n咁都叫宗教信仰自由政策？"},{"pid":"636416fcff7ec49a2ca5d09b75b96da2bfe18bd3","tid":2344640,"uid":146558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f93f60b7e424d14f7d83cd43087de239598f143","tid":2344640,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,